        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "For most NZ tradies, salons and consultants, a professional site typically costs between $1,500 and $3,000 upfront, plus ongoing hosting and support. YourHQ is $2,500 NZD + GST one-time setup plus a monthly Caretaker subscription from $129 NZD + GST, which includes hosting, security, an annual design refresh, and a tier-based dev-time allowance for on-demand updates."
